    <div class="main review-item" id="7617693">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7617693/" class="title-link">定义专业人员的边界</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7617693"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4271688/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4271688-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4271688/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Sun Zoo Tin</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-10-05"
      class="main-meta">2015-10-05 23:29:07</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7617693_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  首先吐槽一下本书的局限： 1. 作为论据的历史和案例可略读或不读，不然很容易分散你的思路； 2. 后半部分很多在重复前文观点，当然你可以把它当作是作者在强调并加深你的记忆。 以上两点也是本类畅销书的通病，如《黑天鹅》、《反脆弱》、《异类》和《引爆点》等，但不阻碍它们...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">19有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7617693_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7617693_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7803801">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7803801/" class="title-link">网络真的使我们变笨了吗？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7803801"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

